  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You spin at a violent speed, while releasing Chakra from every Chakra point on your body. Creating a dome of blue Chakra repelling most attacks. Until the start of your next turn you have a +4 Bonus to AC. If you are subject to a jutsu that requires you to make a Strength or Dexterity saving throw you make the save at advantage. Creatures who are within 5 feet of you when you cast this jutsu must succeed a Strength saving throw, taking 2d8 Force damage and being pushed back 5 feet on a failed save.</p>",
